ue-500\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Automation Engine</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-neutral-400 text-sm\">\n            Automate repetitive tasks with intelligent workflows. Save hours every week with zero-code automation.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Feature 4 -->\n        <div class=\"bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-colors\">\n          <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4\">\n            <i data-lucide=\"lock\" class=\"w-6 h-6 text-blue-500\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Enterprise Security</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-neutral-400 text-sm\">\n            Bank-grade encryption, SSO, and compliance with GDPR, SOC2, and HIPAA standards.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Feature 5 -->\n        <div class=\"bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-colors\">\n          <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4\">\n            <i data-lucide=\"plug\" class=\"w-6 h-6 text-blue-500\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Integrations</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-neutral-400 text-sm\">\n            Connect with 50+ tools you already use. Slack, Salesforce, Jira, and more in one click.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- Feature 6 -->\n        <div class=\"bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-colors\">\n          <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4\">\n            <i data-lucide=\"headphones\" class=\"w-6 h-6 text-blue-500\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">24/7 Support</h3>\n          <p class=\"text-neutral-400 text-sm\">\n            Our dedicated support tea